The paper deals with information theory and communication systems, specifically with encoding and decoding of a Gaussian source under distortion constraints. It also involves the use of side information, which falls under the categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and signal processing (cs.SP). The paper also discusses optimization problems, which could be categorized under networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). Overall, the most likely category is cs.IT, followed by cs.MM, cs.SI, cs.NI, and cs.SP.
